ifier and the expert radiologist. Data Conclusion: Machine learning conducted on MR TA-derived features is a potential tool to characterize adrenal lesions. Level of Evidence: 4. Technical Efficacy: Stage 2. J. Magn. Reson. Imaging 2018.},
